{"tid":2005271,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"信神，信上帝，信佛，信鬼魂，信通靈，信外星人，信未來人","createTime":"2020-05-07T04:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T13:07:42.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e51fd30eb97d10abe74a7fccaaafd66a8d675ae","tid":2005271,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:03:23.000Z","msg":"信神，信上帝，信佛，信鬼魂，信通靈，信外星人，信未來人<br />\n同信活聖有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宇宙咁大，好多野我們唔知，好多野係科學解釋唔到，宇宙肯定有好多神秘野。<br />\n所以我們要信活聖<br />\n活聖聖榮<br />\n<br />\n係活聖嘅國度裏面,我地都係平等嘅<br />\n萬物皆空,淨化心靈才是永恆<br />\n魔鬼從原罪崩裂,是聖靈的哀鳴<br />\n<br />\n末日將至,烈火焚城<br />\n活聖聖靈潔淨大地<br />\n用血清洗叛徒,用血清洗罪孽<br />\n誰要褻瀆聖靈,便是魔鬼!<br />\n我奉神嘅聖名<br />\n除魔滅妖,潔淨大地<br />\n讓愚昧嘅世人知道,神力嘅偉大<br />\n活聖聖榮!<br />\n只要流乾哂身體裏面D血<br />\n就可以得到永生,到達轉點<br />\n感謝活聖救贖"},{"pid":"7af2cf8daa9167407f77add493f388487748cc47","tid":2005271,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UA1KSZq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUA1KSZq.jpg&h=394dda6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjgOAcG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjgOAcG.jpg&h=c6fb4ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vaSNQL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvaSNQL1.jpg&h=7cbabb63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFkoo50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFkoo50.jpg&h=e30173b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"351fd2c922bf9b388da3e773eff61af2fb4e7002","tid":2005271,"uid":10890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"柒Joe忍咗咁耐<br />\n終於要語無倫次咁鳩噏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過見你開喺神秘台<br />\n笑完就算"},{"pid":"ef9eaac0a994bcc77ff52f6340150f8def419df5","tid":2005271,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1